00:30:55,480 --> 00:31:00,630
The best predictor,for example of maintaining an exercise regime
比如 坚持训练课程最好的方法之一

538
00:31:00,870 --> 00:31:02,800
is doing it with other people.
就是和其他人一起进行

539
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:05,060
