书面写下也很有用...等于建立了契约

546
00:31:24,770 --> 00:31:27,140
Write down goals.Divide and conquer.
把目标写下来 分阶段进行

547
00:31:27,390 --> 00:31:28,470
Break down the achievement.
一一击破

548
00:31:28,690 --> 00:31:32,330
Remember Langer's research? Write these things down.
还记得Langer的研究吗 把目标写下来

549
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:35,400
