准许自己为人

552
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:50,340
give yourself permission to procrastinate at times as well;
有时候拖延一下也未尝不可

553
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:54,090
give yourself permission to recover.
允许自己休整

554
00:31:54,690 --> 00:31:56,240
