00:34:08,350 --> 00:34:14,760
this lecture this topic is the most personally meaningful to me.
这节课这一主题对我来说意义最深远

592
00:34:15,850 --> 00:34:22,530
Because in many ways,my shift,my journey from perfectionism-
因为从许多方面 我的转变 从完美主义到...

593
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:24,120
and it's an on-going journey,
这一转变仍在进行

