00:34:33,090 --> 00:34:35,840
is the most intimately linked
这一转变与我的快乐历程

597
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:39,230
with my journey toward becoming happier.
紧密相连

598
00:34:40,530 --> 00:34:46,170
So I want to share with you some personal things
我想给大家讲讲

599
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,930
that I've been through.
我的一些个人经历

600
00:34:48,170 --> 00:34:50,070
Some of them are in my book.
有些已经写在书里了

601
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:54,960
But I want to expand this- the story beyond squash.
我想再扩展一下 不止壁球的故事

602
00:34:56,930 --> 00:35:00,020
So I started playing squash at the age of 11,
我11岁开始打壁球

603
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:04,160
which was after giving up an illustrious,
放弃成为篮球明星

604
00:35:04,390 --> 00:35:06,640
passionate career as a basketball star.
这一前途光明 充满激情的事业

605
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:08,280
It was about that time
那时

606
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:12,480
when I realized that NBA was not going to be a...
我意识到NBA的梦想

607
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:14,100
was not going to happen for me.
无法实现了

608
00:35:15,780 --> 00:35:16,730
I started playing squash
我转而开始打壁球

609
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:19,370
and almost immediately started playing every day.
几乎每天都打

610
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:23,730
My days revolved; my life at that time revolved around squash.
当时我的生活围绕着壁球转

611
00:35:24,050 --> 00:35:27,610
I would wake up at 5 am in the morning and go for a run.
每天早上5点起床 出门跑步

612
00:35:27,910 --> 00:35:31,660
Would come home.Have my food.Go to school.
回到家 吃早餐 上学

613
00:35:31,910 --> 00:35:33,940
Right after school- it was next to the squash,
放学后 我会去打壁球

614
00:35:34,170 --> 00:35:36,630
not far from the squash court,I would go to the squash court,
学校就在壁球场附近 距离不远

615
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:43,030
play with my coach,work out in the gym,play games.
与教练一起练习 在健身房锻炼 打比赛

616
00:35:43,350 --> 00:35:45,350
And then,late afternoon,
一直到傍晚

617
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:48,780
I would go home,do my homework and then go to sleep.
才回家做作业 然后睡觉

618
00:35:49,090 --> 00:35:50,950
For years,this was my pattern.
好几年一直如此

619
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:54,650
It was difficult.It was tough,especially the interval training-
那段时间很苦 很艰难 尤其是间歇训练

620
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:57,560
work out with my coach.
与教练一起锻炼

621
00:35:57,810 --> 00:36:01,280
However,it was nothing- the toughness was nothing compared
但是 这些训练强度与我心理上遇到的问题比

622
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:05,360
to the emotional difficulties at the time.
根本不算什么

623
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:11,660
I was constantly,constantly with almost no recovery,no reprieve
我不断受到压力

624
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,360
I was constantly stressed.
而且几乎没有休整

625
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:17,100
There was always a knot that I felt in my stomach.
我总觉得胃里有个结

626
00:36:18,010 --> 00:36:20,110
It was real,as if there was a ball here.
感觉很真实 就好像有个球在那里

627
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,040
The knot was especially pronounced,
每次训练情况不好

628
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:28,030
especially difficult after a poor performance in practice
与我给自己设定的标准产生距离时

629
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:31,570
when it didn't match to the standards that I had for myself.
这个结尤其明显 尤其难受

630
00:36:32,430 --> 00:36:34,650
And it was almost never matched.
而距离几乎一直存在

631
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:39,180
The knot was at its severest during tournaments.
比赛期间情况尤为严重

632
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:43,160
Very often,I would get to a final of an important tournament
经常 我闯入了一场重要比赛的决赛

633
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:46,020
and choke and lose the final,
突然发挥失常 输了决赛

634
00:36:46,250 --> 00:36:51,200
even at times when I was supposed to win- on paper at least.
哪怕理论上能赢的比赛都输了

635
00:36:51,540 --> 00:36:54,000
That knot didn't go away.
那个结没有消失

636
00:36:54,250 --> 00:36:57,040
When it went away,it was only for very short periods of time.
就算消失 也只是很短的一段时间

637
00:36:57,870 --> 00:37:00,350
But I knew that the knot would go away.
但我相信它会消失的

638
00:37:00,610 --> 00:37:02,730
And I was sustained by the belief,by the vision,
当时有一个信念 一个愿望

639
00:37:02,930 --> 00:37:05,410
by my personal mission at the time of winning
一个目标一直支撑着我

640
00:37:05,620 --> 00:37:07,480
the Israeli National Championships.
要赢得以色列全国锦标赛

641
00:37:07,690 --> 00:37:08,490
I said to myself,
我对自己说

642
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:14,280
"if I win this,then I'll be happy; then I'll be calm.
"如果我赢了 我就会快乐 就会平静

643
00:37:15,410 --> 00:37:17,410
And it's all going to be worth it."
一切付出都是值得的"

644
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:20,480
Why? Because no pain,no gain.
为什么 因为只有付出 才有收获

645
00:37:21,310 --> 00:37:27,280
In 1986,I reached the final of Israeli National Championships
1986年 我闯入了以色列全国锦标赛决赛

646
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,790
and I lost.
但我输了

647
00:37:31,380 --> 00:37:34,560
I was devastated.I was devastated,
我身心交瘁

648
00:37:34,790 --> 00:37:37,590
even though I was the youngest player to ever reach the final,
虽然我是有史以来最年轻的决赛选手

649
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:42,600
even though I'd beaten players higher than me on the rankings.
虽然我击败了排名高于我的选手

650
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:47,050
I was devastated for months.
我一蹶不振好几个月

651
00:37:47,310 --> 00:37:50,400
But still,I went on- no pain,no gain.
不过最终 我还是挺过来了 只有付出 才有收获

652
00:37:50,630 --> 00:37:52,540
And I continued to train and work hard.
我继续刻苦训练

653
00:37:52,780 --> 00:38:00,480
In 1987,I met the same player in the final and this time I won.
1987年 我在决赛中又碰到了同一个对手 这次我赢了

654
00:38:00,780 --> 00:38:05,340
I was ecstatic,joyous,happier than I ever remember myself being
我欣喜若狂 从未如此快乐过

655
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:10,150
And at that moment,I said to myself,"it all paid off.
那一刻 我对自己说"付出终有回报

656
00:38:10,390 --> 00:38:11,910
It was all worth it.
都是值得的

657
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:15,210
Because now I was ready to be happy."
我会变得快乐"

658
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:22,240
I went out with my friends and family,and we celebrated.
我跟亲朋好友外出庆祝

659
00:38:24,090 --> 00:38:28,180
And about 4 hours later after the celebration,I went back home.
庆祝会后4小时 我回到家

660
00:38:28,610 --> 00:38:32,590
I went back home,and wanted to,before going to sleep,
我回到家 睡觉前

661
00:38:32,810 --> 00:38:38,010
just for one last time savor,enjoy that feeling of joy,
想再回味一下

662
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:42,530
of ecstasy,of pure bliss that I earned.
胜利的喜悦与快乐

663
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:46,820
And I sat down on my bed and I suddenly,without any warning,
我坐在床上 突然毫无预警地

664
00:38:47,040 --> 00:38:50,350
the exact same feeling,the exact same emotion,
完全相同的感觉 完全相同的情感

665
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:54,570
the exact same knot returned.
那个结又回来了

666
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:58,320
And I started to cry- not the same tears of joy
我放声大哭 不是4小时前

667
00:38:58,550 --> 00:39:05,530
that I cried 4 hours earlier,but tears of pain and helplessness.
喜极而泣的泪水 而且痛苦无助的泪水

668
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:08,160
The knot returned.
那个结又回来了

669
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:09,960
And I thought,"well,maybe it's the high follow...
我想"也许这是高潮后的失落"

670
00:39:10,180 --> 00:39:12,950
It's the low following high." And I hoped it would go away.
我指望结会再消失

671
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:14,440
But it didn't go away.
但它没有

672
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:15,300
And a few weeks later,
几周后

673
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:18,430
I realized what it was and this time I really nailed it.
我意识到它究竟是什么 这一次我彻底搞清楚了

674
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:19,670
I understood.
我明白了

675
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:24,670
I would have to be the world champion to really be happy.
我要成为世界冠军才能真正快乐

676
00:39:25,020 --> 00:39:26,590
I graduated from high school.
高中毕业后

677
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:30,270
I had two years before I had to enlist in the military.
离我入伍服役还有2年空余时间

678
00:39:30,540 --> 00:39:33,100
And I took off to England.
我去了英格兰

679
00:39:34,290 --> 00:39:36,460
In England,I lived in London
住在伦敦

680
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:40,810
and joined Stripes which was the squash club in Ealing Broadway,
加入了位于Ealing大道的Stripes壁球俱乐部

681
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:44,890
where Jansher Khan,world champion at the time used to train.
当时世界冠军Jansher Khan常常在那训练

682
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:48,480
Because I said,"this is my goal; this is my objective."
因为我对自己说"这是我的目标"

683
00:39:48,720 --> 00:39:50,510
And I would come in every single day
我每天都去俱乐部

684
00:39:50,750 --> 00:39:53,860
and watch Jansher Khan and imitate him.
看Jansher Khan训练 模仿他

685
00:39:54,100 --> 00:39:56,350
Whatever he did,I would do.
无论他做什么 我都照做

686
00:39:56,580 --> 00:40:02,990
So he ran 7 miles each morning; I would ran 7 miles each morning.
他每天早上跑7英里 我也每天早上跑7英里

687
00:40:03,220 --> 00:40:05,090
He would go to the court,work out in the gym;
他去壁球场 去健身房锻炼

688
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:07,400
I did exactly what he did.
我都照做

689
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:11,840
He played numerous games with other players;
他与其他选手进行无数场比赛

690
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:14,640
I would play numerous games with other players.
我也与其他选手进行无数场比赛

691
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:17,620
And he had training partners.
他有训练搭档

692
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:20,030
And I wasn't good enough at that time to be his training partner,
当时我水平还不够成为他的训练搭档

693
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:22,470
so I would just hang out there and once in a while,
所以只是偶尔去一次

694
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:25,180
once in a while when there was no one around,he would say,
有时候 只有我们两人时 他会说

695
00:40:25,470 --> 00:40:28,370
"come,Tal,let's play a little bit." And we would play.
"来吧 Tal 我们对打看看" 于是我们会打一会儿

696
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:32,150
And I went back to the drawing board after each game with him.
每次与他比赛后 我都会从头再来

697
00:40:32,390 --> 00:40:34,410
And I would play harder and train harder.
更努力的打球 更努力的练习

698
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:38,200
Just what he did- because to be like him,
因为要像他那样

699
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:41,170
to be the world champion,I would have to train like him.
成为世界冠军 我就必须像他一样训练

700
00:40:42,130 --> 00:40:46,950
And I trained harder and harder.And I got better and better.
我训练越来越刻苦 表现也越来越好

701
00:40:48,650 --> 00:40:50,390
And after about six months,
六个月后

702
00:40:50,640 --> 00:40:54,090
I became good enough to be one of his training partners.
我的水平能够成为他的训练搭档了

703
00:40:54,330 --> 00:40:56,710
And after a year,I became his regular training partner.
一年后 我成为了他的常规搭档

704
00:40:56,930 --> 00:40:58,900
I would travel with him around the world.
我跟着他去了世界各地

705
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:03,610
Wherever he would play tournaments,we would train before.
只要他有比赛 我们都会进行训练

706
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:08,920
However,injuries began to creep in.Why?
但是 伤痛开始出现 为什么

707
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:11,610
Because Jansher had built up from,literally the age of three,
因为Jansher从三岁就开始锻炼

708
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:13,920
he built up his stamina,his fitness;
他的耐力体格 都是日积月累锻炼出来的

709
00:41:14,180 --> 00:41:17,300
and for me,it was all or nothing.
而我 要么全有要么全无

710
00:41:17,610 --> 00:41:20,160
Either I trained like an amateur or don't train at all,
要么进行业余训练 要么完全不训练

711
00:41:20,410 --> 00:41:23,230
or I trained like the world champion.
要么像世界冠军一样训练

712
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:26,890
And my body couldn't handle it.And I started injuries.
我的身体无法承受 开始出现伤痛

713
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:31,620
Initially,mild injuries- ankle.So I took two days off.
一开始 只是踝关节小伤 所以我休息了两天

714
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,730
Or my knee started hurting a little bit-
如果膝盖有伤

715
00:41:33,950 --> 00:41:35,790
you know,three,four days off.
那就休息三四天

716
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:38,650
Back was a bit uncomfortable.Nothing serious.
恢复训练以后会有一点不舒服 不过不严重

717
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:41,740
I would go back to training.All or nothing.
我会继续训练 要么全有要么全无

718
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:44,960
Either I don't train at all or I train like the world champion.
要么不训练 要么像世界冠军一样训练

719
00:41:45,200 --> 00:41:46,960
Cause I want to be like him.
因为我想成为他那样

720
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:55,220
And I continue doing that for 4 years.Injuries on and off.
就这样坚持了4年 伤痛时有出现

721
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:59,210
Getting more and more severe,until the age of 20.21-
越来越严重 直到我20 21岁时

722
00:41:59,420 --> 00:42:01,980
the doctor told me,"you have a choice.
医生告诉我"你面临一个选择

723
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:05,380
You can continue training and playing professional squash,
你可以继续训练 打职业壁球赛

724
00:42:06,610 --> 00:42:08,500
but then you are risking your back
但你的背部会非常危险

725
00:42:08,710 --> 00:42:11,710
and you probably need to be operated on very soon.
可能很快就需要动手术

726
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:14,700
Or you can give up professional squash."
要么就放弃职业壁球"

727
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:20,840
with an extremely heavy heart,I gave up professional squash.
怀着沉重的心情 我放弃了职业壁球

728
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:25,260
I gave up my dream,applied to college,and came here.
放弃了我的梦想 申请入学 来到了这里

729
00:42:26,690 --> 00:42:29,640
Here,the exact same pattern continued-
同样的模式又发生了

730
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:31,400
only before it was squash;
只不过以前是壁球

731
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:36,170
now it was academics that became the central part of my life.
现在学术成了我生活的中心

732
00:42:36,530 --> 00:42:40,540
The knot returned,very shortly after freshman week.
开学才一周 那个结又回来了

733
00:42:40,870 --> 00:42:43,820
Because every paper had to be perfect.
因为每一篇论文我都力求完美

734
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:49,570
Every word had to be read and summarized.
书上每一个词都要阅读并总结

735
00:42:50,250 --> 00:42:54,130
Every assignment had to be executed immaculately.
每一次作业都要毫无偏差地完成

736
00:42:54,380 --> 00:42:58,870
All or nothing.And I was unhappy.
要么全有 要么全无 我不快乐

737
00:43:00,070 --> 00:43:03,140
And it was on one day during my sophomore year.
在我大二时的某一天

738
00:43:03,530 --> 00:43:08,110
I was a 23 year old sophomore,where I said to myself,
当时我23岁 我对自己说

739
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:15,660
"enough.Enough.Here I am,in such a wonderful place,
"够了 我身在名校

740
00:43:16,040 --> 00:43:20,300
with such wonderful students,such wonderful teachers.
有这么多出色的同学 优秀的导师

741
00:43:22,480 --> 00:43:26,130
Such a privilege.And I am so unhappy.
应该感到荣幸 但我一点也不快乐"

742
00:43:27,580 --> 00:43:30,740
I don't think it is something that is external.
我觉得这不是外部问题

743
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,910
I must understand myself better.
我必须更好地了解自己

744
00:43:33,170 --> 00:43:34,850
And it was at that point that
于是

745
00:43:35,060 --> 00:43:41,590
I decided to switch my concentration to philosophy and psychology
我转而研究哲学与心理学

746
00:43:42,940 --> 00:43:47,250
wanting to understand the meaning of a happy life,
希望了解快乐生活的意义

747
00:43:47,490 --> 00:43:49,400
wanting to understand how I could become happier
了解如何才能更快乐

748
00:43:49,620 --> 00:43:50,560
and why I was not.
为什么我不快乐

749
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:52,560
And it was very quickly that I realized,
很快我意识到

750
00:43:52,790 --> 00:43:56,810
that I understood that I was engaged,
我发现自己从事...

751
00:43:57,010 --> 00:43:59,580
or suffering from something that is so common,
或者说遭受到某种普遍

752
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:05,820
so pervasive and so misunderstood.
且错误的观念折磨

753
00:44:06,590 --> 00:44:08,620
Perfectionism.
完美主义

754
00:44:09,650 --> 00:44:11,530
This is what I want to talk about today,
这就是今天

755
00:44:11,750 --> 00:44:14,730
and what I want to talk about in the next lecture.
及下节课的主题

756
00:44:14,970 --> 00:44:16,660
This notion of perfectionism
完美主义的概念

757
00:44:16,890 --> 00:44:20,370
and what the research has to say about it.
以及对完美主义的研究

758
00:44:20,630 --> 00:44:23,000
Now there is no perfectionist,
人无完人

759
00:44:23,230 --> 00:44:25,130
there is no one person who is on this extreme,
没有人会处于糟糕的极端

760
00:44:25,350 --> 00:44:28,000
nor there is a person who's on the excellence extreme
也没有人会处于卓越的极端

761
00:44:28,200 --> 00:44:29,710
which I will depict later.
这点我等会儿会细讲

762
00:44:29,970 --> 00:44:32,730
The key is how do I become happier
关键是 如何变得更快乐

763
00:44:33,020 --> 00:44:38,160
and I become happier by being less and less perfectionistic.
随着我渐渐脱离完美主义 我变得更快乐了

764
00:44:38,390 --> 00:44:41,620
Perfectionism is not about giving up ambition.
完美主义并不是说要放弃志向

765
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:43,310
I'm as ambitious,
我有志向

766
00:44:43,590 --> 00:44:49,120
or possibly more ambitious than I was at age of 16 or 23.
甚至可能比16或23岁时志向更远大

767
00:44:50,670 --> 00:44:52,670
It's about having a different approach
而是说对人生历程

768
00:44:52,920 --> 00:44:54,350
toward the journey of our life,
对走出的每一步 尤其是对失败

769
00:44:54,570 --> 00:44:59,920
toward each step of the way- specifically,toward failure.
采取一种不同的方法与态度

770
00:45:01,870 --> 00:45:04,040
So what I'm going to talk about is first of all,
所以我要谈的第一点

771
00:45:04,250 --> 00:45:05,620
define it so that we understand it.
先定义以便理解

772
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,720
Because it is misunderstood.
因为它常常被误解

773
00:45:07,990 --> 00:45:09,800
I'm going to talk about characteristics.
我会谈谈完美主义的特征

774
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:12,110
We are going to get to that next time only.
我们下节课才会讲

775
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:15,790
The characteristics- what it means to be a perfectionist?
特征...成为完美主义者代表了什么?

776
00:45:16,140 --> 00:45:18,660
Then I'm going to talk about the consequences.
然后我还会讲讲后果

777
00:45:20,310 --> 00:45:26,170
And then,how it's possible to be both successful and happy.
以及如何保持成功与快乐的平衡

778
00:45:26,420 --> 00:45:29,100
Again,the question we ask in goal setting lecture,
我们在目标设定课上问的问题

779
00:45:29,320 --> 00:45:31,700
the question that essentially we are asking throughout the class-
这一问题我们在课堂上会经常重复

780
00:45:31,930 --> 00:45:34,180
it's not about giving up success;
不是为了放弃成功

781
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:38,160
it's not about giving up the conventional currency.But
放弃日常生活中的金钱

782
00:45:38,380 --> 00:45:42,210
it's about also enjoying the ultimate currency more importantly.
而是更好地享受我们的幸福

783
00:45:42,400 --> 00:45:44,390
Because it is the ultimate currency.
因为它是终极货币

784
00:45:45,980 --> 00:45:47,950
Then we understand what is the source of perfection;
然后我们理解完美主义的源头是什么

785
00:45:48,150 --> 00:45:48,600
where does it come.
它来自哪里

786
00:45:48,810 --> 00:45:50,710
Because if we understand where it comes from,
因为如果我们了解了它是如何产生的

787
00:45:50,910 --> 00:45:54,610
we are more likely to be able to overcome it.
才更有可能克服它

788
00:45:55,910 --> 00:45:59,660
And then,most importantly,how do we overcome it?
然后 最重要的是 如何克服

789
00:45:59,880 --> 00:46:03,410
And how do we help other people overcome perfectionism?
如何帮助别人克服完美主义

790
00:46:03,650 --> 00:46:06,870
And again,not giving up their ambition,not giving up hard work,
不是让他们放弃志向 或者停止努力工作

791
00:46:07,290 --> 00:46:10,800
not giving up pain of failure- because that's inevitable.
也不是消除失败时的痛苦 这是不可避免的

792
00:46:11,030 --> 00:46:14,990
But simply have a more rational,a more helpful,
而是获得一种更理性 更有益

793
00:46:15,240 --> 00:46:18,090
a more empowering approach toward failure.
更可控的处理失败的方法

794
00:46:20,590 --> 00:46:28,770
OK.So let's get to work.I need a volunteer.
好了 我们开始前 我需要一名志愿者

795
00:46:29,130 --> 00:46:31,300
I need a volunteer,but before you put your hand up,
你们举手前 注意我的要求

796
00:46:31,540 --> 00:46:34,480
it's a very special kind of volunteer.
我要一个很特别的志愿者

797
00:46:34,790 --> 00:46:42,060
I need a volunteer who is a very good artist,
我需要一个很棒的艺术家

798
00:46:42,330 --> 00:46:46,650
a volunteer who can draw really well.
绘画非常出色

799
00:46:48,990 --> 00:46:52,980
No pressure here,right? A volunteer who can draw really well
不要有压力 好吗 要一个画画很棒

800
00:46:53,470 --> 00:46:57,390
and who will actually come here and demonstrate.
且愿意上来展示的志愿者

801
00:46:57,610 --> 00:47:00,580
Now remember it takes courage to come up to the stage
要上台来需要一定勇气

802
00:47:00,780 --> 00:47:03,080
but courage is not about not having fear;
有勇气并不代表不害怕

803
00:47:03,340 --> 00:47:06,740
it's about having fear and going ahead anyway.
而是害怕但仍勇往直前

804
00:47:07,320 --> 00:47:10,760
So do I have a volunteer? I have a volunteer.
有人自愿吗 有一个志愿者

805
00:47:11,000 --> 00:47:18,440
Won't you come up? (Applause)
你上来好吗

806
00:47:24,750 --> 00:47:28,980
OK.Hi.What's your name? Vincent.
你好 怎么称呼 Vincent

807
00:47:29,210 --> 00:47:32,230
Are you a VS concentrator? (Inaudible)
你是VS专业的吗

808
00:47:32,450 --> 00:47:34,600
Don't tell me you are an economics.OK.
别告诉我你是学经济的 好的

809
00:47:34,820 --> 00:47:40,910
What are you? Biology.OK.Good.(Laugh) All right.
那你是什么专业的?生物 很好

810
00:47:41,120 --> 00:47:42,890
So biology- you have to draw many diagrams.
生物学也要画许多图表

811
00:47:43,060 --> 00:47:43,600
That's why I was...
所以我...

812
00:47:43,790 --> 00:47:46,300
Well in Ec you also have to draw diagrams I guess.
经济学也得画图标吧

813
00:47:46,520 --> 00:47:48,190
So it would've been fine,too.
所以也没关系

814
00:47:48,460 --> 00:47:49,740
All right.Are you ready for this?
好了 准备好了吗

815
00:47:49,930 --> 00:47:52,050
You still have the opportunity to going sit down.
最后一次机会让你回到位子上

816
00:47:52,880 --> 00:47:53,750
You are sure you want to...
你确定要...

817
00:47:53,960 --> 00:47:57,600
(Vincent: But I want to conquer my fear.) All right! Yes,good.
- 但我想战胜恐惧 - 好的 很好

818
00:48:01,650 --> 00:48:05,510
All right.Are you ready for this,Vincent? You sure? All right.
好了 准备好了吗 Vincent?你确定 好

819
00:48:05,690 --> 00:48:07,310
Here's what I want you to do now.
以下是我要你做的

820
00:48:08,590 --> 00:48:10,370
I don't know if I want to do this to you though,you know.
我不知道是不是真的想这样对你

821
00:48:10,580 --> 00:48:12,120
All right,but I am going to do it to you anyway.
但是我也只能这样了

822
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:18,930
I want you to draw here on this part of the board.
请在黑板的这边画...

823
00:48:19,150 --> 00:48:19,770
I want you to draw...
请画...

824
00:48:19,920 --> 00:48:22,660
Are you ready for this? You sure? OK.
准备好了吗 你确定?好的

825
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:28,850
I want you to draw a circle.
请画一个圆

826
00:48:29,550 --> 00:48:33,110
Take your time.Take your time.No hurry.
慢慢来 不急

827
00:48:33,350 --> 00:48:35,290
You can also erase and put back.
可以擦了重画

828
00:48:35,320 --> 00:48:37,540
But I want to you draw- give your best shot here-
拿出你的看家本事

829
00:48:37,770 --> 00:48:40,430
I want you to draw a circle.
画一个圆

830
00:48:41,620 --> 00:48:43,750
We have half an hour.No hurry.
我们还有半小时时间 不急

831
00:48:44,880 --> 00:48:50,880
The meantime we'll meditate.(Laugh) Yeah.
我们边冥想边等你

832
00:48:51,110 --> 00:48:52,870
I didn't mean it literally half an hour,
我不是真的说半小时

833
00:48:53,090 --> 00:49:11,660
but...OK.(Laugh) Use it as a time-in.That's all.
不过...好的 就当是练习时间

834
00:49:12,250 --> 00:49:19,950
A circle! Vincent,well done! Ooh hoo! (Applause)
一个圆 Vincent 画得漂亮

835
00:49:20,260 --> 00:49:20,920
You are not done yet.
还没完呢

836
00:49:21,090 --> 00:49:23,760
Hey hey! Woah woah woah woah.
等等

837
00:49:24,010 --> 00:49:25,280
Don't run away on me now.
先别急着走

838
00:49:25,500 --> 00:49:28,680
OK.So I'm putting a line here.
好的 我在这画一条线

839
00:49:29,250 --> 00:49:32,780
What I'd like you to do here is draw something else.
这边要画其他东西

840
00:49:33,010 --> 00:49:37,790
So you are ready for it? I would like you to draw another circle,
